title: 2 cats in NY become first US pets to test positive for virus
description: Two pet cats in New York state have tested positive for the coronavirus, marking the first confirmed cases in companion animals in the United States
content:
NEW YORK -- 
Two pet cats in New York state have tested positive for the coronavirus, marking the first confirmed cases in companion animals in the United States, federal officials said Wednesday.
